{"tid":1852152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩騙徒","createTime":"2020-01-30T10:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T12:54:16.000Z","uid":322434,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6e700affcd2c1cb99becbebfcf833bc4247e6efc","tid":1852152,"uid":322434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"網上口罩騙徒<br />\n<br />\n電話  （以數字小至大排序）：<br />\n⚠ #盡量咪用Alipay或Payme過數 ⚠<br />\n53xxxx30<br />\n54323164<br />\n54363124<br />\n54623164<br />\n54653554<br />\n55233959<br />\n55617573 Lam M** K** E*<br />\n55724019 Chan M** Y*<br />\n56252889<br />\n<br />\n61xxxx75<br />\n61756004<br />\n61976414 Lau Y** C**<br />\n6302-3094<br />\n63xxxx15<br />\n64375378<br />\n64376616<br />\n69xxxx57 <br />\n65342721 Lee K T<br />\n65324512 So P* H***<br />\n66438420 Lau Y T<br />\n66439220<br />\n67446486 Cheung Y** P***<br />\n67495420<br />\n68211118 Anna Wong 批谷走數王<br />\n69307014 Tang S** W*<br />\n<br />\n90854749<br />\n90886049 Tsoi C** Y* K**<br />\n91041992 Yuen H** C**<br />\n95473028 Poon W** L**<br />\n9582-5521<br />\n96599044 Yu C** P**<br />\n98871412<br />\n<br />\n銀行戶口號碼（以數字小至大排序）：<br />\n012-552-1-0271410 Tam Wxx Pxx (BOC) <br />\n012-572-2-0062539 Chiu Sxxx Yxxc (BOC) <br />\n012-787-1-005719-0 Lau Chi Chau (BOC) <br />\n012-805-1-0479702 Ng Hui Ying (BOC)<br />\n012-831-1-0482375 Lee Kwok Tung (BOC) <br />\n325-841195-668 Chan Hiu Kwan (Hang Seng)<br />\n381-208545-882 (Hang Seng) <br />\n<br />\n當然，絕對相信騙徒會繼續用其他太空卡同其他戶口號碼，所以各位爸爸媽媽要小心提防騙徒呀！<br />\n<br />\n另外Carousell有大量騙徒，各位買口罩要小心，當你問佢有冇貨既時候佢死都會同你講有貨，之後問佢有幾盒？佢會話有10盒左右，等你過左數後佢就話買多左10幾盒，合共有20幾盒之後再問你要唔要，當你過左數後佢就會人間蒸發.....<br />\n#我就係Carousell受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf7de05ee9799c1717173dd9abba11e663e7e45","tid":1852152,"uid":129278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2cf435476d63c0d72ec1